==Useful Info==
'''Orc high priests''' are similar to [[orc priest]]s, but are significantly more dangerous. Along with their [[smite]] attack, they can summon dangerous demons and heal themselves as well as their allies. They are often found in the [[Orcish Mines]] (but may appear earlier).

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
Most characters first exploring the Orcish Mines aren't prepared for dealing with several [[tier-3 demon]]s along with a horde of heavily armed orcs, so try not to give orc high priests time to summon much. Don't be afraid to run if a fight suddenly gets overwhelmingly dangerous.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], orc high priests could [[see invisible]].

